  "mode": "guided_story",
  "screens": [
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s016",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "决策树在构建时，需要决定先问哪个问题。",
        "比如：先问年龄，还是先问收入？"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "entropy"
      ],
      "id": "s017",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "entropy"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "一个好的问题，应该能最大程度地降低不确定性。",
        "如何量化“不确定性”？用<term id=\"entropy\">熵</term>。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "entropy"
      ],
      "id": "s018",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "想象一个信息源，只发送字母'a'和'b'。",
        "如果两个字母出现概率各占一半，你猜下一个是什么？"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "entropy"
      ],
      "id": "s019",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "非常不确定，对吧？这时熵是1。",
        "如果它总是发'a'，你完全确定，熵就是0。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "entropy"
      ],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "H(S) = -\\sum_i p_i \\log_2(p_i)",
        "spoken": "熵等于负的每个概率乘以以2为底该概率的对数之和。"
      },
      "id": "s020",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "熵的公式是：",
        "$$ H(S) = -\\sum_i p_i \\log_2(p_i) $$"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "entropy"
      ],
      "id": "s021",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "回到我们的14条数据：9个有电脑，5个没有。",
        "计算这个数据集的熵。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "entropy"
      ],
      "id": "s022",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "P(有电脑) = 9/14, P(无电脑) = 5/14。",
        "熵 = -(9/14)*log₂(9/14) - (5/14)*log₂(5/14) ≈ 0.940"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "entropy"
      ],
      "id": "s023",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "现在，如果我们用一个特征（比如年龄）来划分数据，",
        "划分后每个子集的熵会降低。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "information_gain"
      ],
      "id": "s024",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "information_gain"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "划分后熵的减少量，就是<term id=\"information_gain\">信息增益</term>。",
        "决策树会优先选择信息增益最大的特征。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "exercise": {
        "answer": 0,
        "explanation": "所有样本属于同一类，不确定性为0，所以熵为0。",
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "options": [
          "0",
          "1",
          "取决于类别数量"
        ],
        "prompt": "一个数据集中所有样本都属于同一类别，它的熵是多少？"
      },
      "focus_terms": [
        "entropy"
      ],
      "id": "s025",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [],
      "type": "exercise"
    }
  ],
  "sequence_id": "step3",
  "source": {
    "plain_text": "Entropy measures uncertainty. Information gain is the reduction in entropy after a split.",
    "related": [
      "decision tree",
      "impurity"
    ]
  },
  "target_language": "zh-CN",
  "term_catalog": {
    "entropy": {
      "aliases": [
        "Entropy",
        "Shannon Entropy"
      ],
      "display": "熵",
      "gloss": "衡量一个系统不确定性或混乱程度的指标。熵越大，越不确定。"
    },
    "information_gain": {
      "aliases": [
        "Information Gain"
      ],
      "display": "信息增益",
      "gloss": "使用某个特征进行划分后，熵减少的量。增益越大，划分效果越好。"
    }
